divs: Sighting DetailsHello, mate. I'm from downunder. Listen to this story MUFON.com. I was out boxing a kangaroo when I saw some lights approaching. I looked up then down again and saw that was in the air. I punched one of the lights in the face then it let me go. My trusty kangaroo caught me and I bounced away with him. It was crazy mate. I think the lights were actually just my parents with flashlights and th trampoline would account for bouncing, but I don't care.
Summary: It was freaking crazy! Lights everywhere.
